Jeugdhuis de Faar, Meerhout Belgium

Play with or against friends, explore the map and find usefull hidden pathways and gadgets.

Overview & radar of the map included.

Hint 1: Remember to flush.

Hint 2: Watch (and listen) out for falling bombs, seek shelter underground or in the woods!

Hint 3: Be curious.

Hint 4: Play some music!


Recommended players: 6-20



Credits:
* Fabia, Octavia, Bus & TV by Dinus Saurus
* Les Paul Guitar, Jack Daniels & Stella Artois by johny[SRKA]

* Realisation @ Jeugdhuis de Faar


For more information and comments please contact me.

If you wanna use this map on your server go ahead, contact me and i'll join.


Greetings,
